Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RRRRRRRYYYEEEEEEEE！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙空間？哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從肺部噴出空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過產生的氣壓改變軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去地球！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結…結冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空氣結冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦離開人體 就結冰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法改變軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回不去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡茲再也沒能回到地球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他變成了介於礦石和生物的中間生命體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在宇宙空間無盡地徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 想死也死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逐漸地 卡茲放棄思考了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:55.35,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(640,590)\be4}紐約郊外 1939年4月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:15:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我們在天上的父
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}願人尊您之聖名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}願您的國降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}願您的意旨行在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}如同行在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:10.12,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,600)\be4}喬瑟夫·喬斯達（1920年～1939年）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永別了 JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在想來 跟你認識了才半年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我一輩子都不會忘記你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉娜小姐 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要著涼了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再留一會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜猜我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 各位 我好不容易回到紐約
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.30,0:16:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼都沒人來接我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後問了一下 你們都到墓地參加葬禮來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我好找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 莉莎莉莎老師 傷好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅西納也在呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呀 還是想找修特羅哈姆弄個更好使的手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 這形勢看來要跟德國開戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你是什麼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘋漢 不知道看看場合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘋漢？你說瘋漢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛才喊我瘋漢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了 走開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}別麻煩到人家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好了 聽我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丫的 剛才喊我瘋子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 JoJo還活著！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活著？等等 為什麼看到我那麼吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.93,0:17:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個個都撞鬼似的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我的名字刻在墓碑上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難…難道這葬禮…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo 你的傷還沒好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要淋雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.47,0:17:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 撐傘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是CJQ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你無名指上的戒指是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那麼你們也不知道我老婆了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆呀 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一上來就這樣介紹人家…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘎 好害羞 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對你個頭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候我被火山連岩石一起衝上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩石剛好成了保護壁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大難不死掉進海裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給威尼斯的漁船救上岸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後來的兩星期 你在威尼斯照顧我養傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些事情 他們好像都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的有發電報嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電…電報…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯！你答應過的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這樣嘎達嘎達的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起！我忘記了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OH NO！難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你個婆娘的腦子怎麼長的！等著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都說對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起有用的話還要警察幹什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo…
